A man is in a critical condition after he was shot at twice by an unknown man in Florida Park on Wednesday.It is reported that the shooting happened around 05:45 when the twenty-one-year-old man was sleeping. He was woken up by a scream from his father, as he ran through the perpetrator shot him twice.He was found in a critical condition and was stabilised before being airlifted to a specialised hospital in Gauteng for further treatment.Police are still investigating the incident.-TNA Reporter